verbose_text: To further investigate the biological significance of the CK1gamma2 / IRS4 axis, we generated U2OS / MTX300 cells stably overexpressing vector, CK1gamma2, IRS4-WT, IRS4-S859A, CK1gamma2 and IRS4-WT, or CK1gamma2 and IRS4-S859A.
